original_title: Back in the Saddle - Fascinating Aïda in Edinburgh
overview: Fascinating Aïda are a three woman (Dillie Keane, Adele Anderson and Liza Pulman) cabaret act that have been performing for over 30 years. This show was recorded live at the Edinburgh Festival Fringe in 2016, in George Square Gardens.
title: Back in the Saddle - Fascinating Aïda in Edinburgh
